      <p>The International Society of Sports Nutrition (ISSN) position stand on BCAAs states that <strong>supplementation before and after exercise can reduce exercise-induced muscle damage, promote muscle protein synthesis, and accelerate recovery</strong>. Effective doses range from 3-10g, with leucine being the most critical component.</p>
      <cite>Journal of the International Society of Sports Nutrition — BCAA Position Stand</cite>
    </div>

